TFVC Workspace Manager
Copyright 2026 Gonzalo Berterame

This product was originally created by Gonzalo Berterame.

TFVC Workspace Manager is a tool intended to simplify the operational
management of TFVC workspaces in Azure DevOps, including workspace
exploration, pending changes inspection, lock inspection, and controlled
undo/unlock operations with logging and auditing support.

